## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3397-104">默认情况下，WMI 方法名称将是目标方法的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-104">By default, the WMI method name will be the name of the target method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-105">此属性的父类<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>，包括名称参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-105">The parent class of this attribute, <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>, includes a Name parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-106">该参数可用于更改而无需更改您的内部方法名称通过 WMI 公开的方法的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-106">You can use that parameter to change the name of the method that is exposed through WMI without changing your internal method name.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3397-107">方法必须是公共的它可以是静态方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-107">The method must be public and it may be static.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-108">它可以包含任意组合的 [in]、 [out]，[in/out]，数组或对象引用参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-108">It can include any combination of [in], [out], [in/out], array or object reference parameters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-109">数组参数不能为多维或交错由于 WMI 施加的限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-109">Array parameters cannot be multidimensional or jagged because of limitations imposed by WMI.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3397-110">该方法的返回类型可以是： void、 标量、 字符串、 日期时间或对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-110">The return type of the method can be: void, scalar, string, datetime or object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-111">它不能为数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-111">It cannot be an array.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3397-112">下面的示例演示如何将标记用 ManagementTask 特性来向 WMI 公开方法的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-112">The following example shows how to mark a method with the ManagementTask attribute to expose the method to WMI.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3397-113">该方法将显示在 WMI 中为 ResetCounters。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3397-113">The method will show up in WMI as ResetCounters.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementTask attribute to specify that a method  
// is exposed to WMI through this provider. Consumers will be  
// able to execute this method through WMI.  
[ManagementTask]  
public void ResetCounters()  
{  
    counter.Reset();  
}  
```
